member.name: CMSG_KEY_AGREE_KEY_ENCRYPT_INFO
member.summary: The CMSG_KEY_AGREE_KEY_ENCRYPT_INFO structure contains the encrypted key for a key agreement recipient of an enveloped message. The structure references this structure.

member.name: CMSG_KEY_AGREE_KEY_ENCRYPT_INFO.cbSize
member.summary: The size, in bytes, of this structure.

member.name: CMSG_KEY_AGREE_KEY_ENCRYPT_INFO.EncryptedKey
member.summary: A CRYPT_DATA_BLOB structure that contains the session key encrypted by the negotiated key of the recipient.
